Package: backup-at-scripts
Architecture: all
Depends: bash (>= 4.3), util-linux(>=2.25.2), at, ${misc:Depends}
Description: lixbackups AT backup scripts
 A number of at job scheduler lixbackups backup scripts. Covers adhoc, daily,
 selective and weekly backups. Also provides variations on these for swoc
 locking and shutdown after backup.
